Invocation Name: defense acquisition university
des:
You can use this official Defense Acquisition University (DAU) Skill to learn about DAU Events, Latest News, Blogs, Flash Briefings, Campus Operating Status, and Course Schedules at all the DAU locations. Please make sure to spell out the course as "A C Q” or “C O N".

We’d like your feedback on this version of the DAU Skill, including what functionality would make it more valuable to you.
